### Sambandh API examples — chat flow

@host = http://localhost:3010
@token = PASTE_TOKEN

### Get my conversations
GET {{host}}/api/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Start a chat with another verified user
POST {{host}}/api/chat/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "withUserId": "OTHER_USER_ID",
  "anonymous": false,
  "intent": "dating"
}

###

### Get messages for a chat
GET {{host}}/api/chat/PASTE_CHAT_ID/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Send a message
POST {{host}}/api/chat/PASTE_CHAT_ID/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Hey! Saw you also did the Hampta Pass — how was it?"
}

###

### Reveal identity in anonymous chat (mutual consent required)
POST {{host}}/api/chat/PASTE_CHAT_ID/reveal
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### --- Payment flow ---

### Create order for join fee
POST {{host}}/api/payment/create-order
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Response will include:
### { "orderId": "order_xxx", "amount": 100, "amountCHF": 1, "currency": "CHF", ... }
### Use this in Razorpay Checkout on the frontend.

###

### Verify payment after Razorpay returns success
POST {{host}}/api/payment/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "razorpay_order_id": "order_xxx",
  "razorpay_payment_id": "pay_xxx",
  "razorpay_signature": "xxx"
}

###
